Pooled / Silo / Hybrid (real workflow) — 10/day × 180d × 500 runs/tier
Providers: 1 unlimited @ 40% start / 4 softs @ 15% each. Bet routing 30% / 17.5%×4.
Hybrid = unlimited pooled, softs siloed for sizing, any soft profit above starting is arbed to unlimited.
Stake schedule: dynamic cap+maxK per current bankroll (matches dynamic_stake_sim).

